div.div: No, it worked for MediaFusion. Other addons only return the flag, so there's nothing you can do about that. The flag emoji will always be parsed as Hindi.
With TPB+ specifically, all results end up being parsed as cached, even if they may not be cached. This is because of the + in the name of the TPB+ addon.

You can put the TPB manifest url into StremThru, and configure it with your debrid service. You then put the StremThru manifest URL, into AIOStreams. I've just tried this and it works. The 'cached only' settings on StremThru and AIOStreams won't conflict, but if you set cached only on StremThru, that overrides it on AIOStreams as AIOStreams will fetch from the cached only StremThru addon.

The second season of Solo Leveling. Mastering his new abilities in secret, Jin-U must battle humanity's toughest foes to save his mother. (Source: Crunchyroll News)
Episodes included in the manga's seventh and tenth volume.

High-school beauty Umaru seems like the perfect teen wunderkind, but she's hiding a shocking double life. As soon as she gets home, she becomes a junk-food-inhaling, soda-guzzling, video-game-addicted slob. The only one who sees this unsavory side of Umaru is her beleaguered older brother Taihei, who does his best to keep up with his work while trying to get his little sister to behave like a decent member of society. As she makes new friends and gets into a number of wacky situations, Umaru will continue to fight for her right to stay up all night binging potato chips and anime. (Source: Anime News Network)

Struck by an enemys arrow, the powerless Prince Davey ORowane falls into a coma. His soul travels to a place where the greatest of the great gatherthe honorable Hall of Heroes. There a thousand years pass as Davey undergoes excruciating training under their watchful eyes to become a hero too strong for his own good. Now back to his timeline and his kingdom, hes wide awake and the enemies hiding in the kings court better be prepared. The prince they had dismissed is now their biggest threat!
(Source: Tapas)
Wan Le Ah! Ndi De Ruanfan Zhangfu Ju Ran Wu Di

The Earthling Xiao Tian was on the verge of death when he was summoned by Empress Zi Ruoyan of the Great Yan Dynasty to become her consort, and he was offered the "Strongest Supremacy System." But Xiao Tian only wants to be a lazy husband for the Empress! So he resolutely rejected the System, but he didn't expect that the Supremacy System would become the Begging Lapdog System instead!?

(Source: Fanqie Manhua, translated)

Dowan Ha is a bullied gamer, whose bullies force him to grind to obtain in-game items for them. After one such bully demands that Dowan obtain an impossibly rare item for him or be beaten in front of the prettiest girl in school, Dowan games day and night for a week until he drops dead from exhaustion. However, as soon as he dies, he respawns back in his classroom one week before his death. Everything is the same as it was before, except now he has all the skills hes acquired from the games hes played in real life! Will Dowan be able to use his newfound abilities and gamified existence to defeat his bullies?
(Source: WEBTOONS)
Comedy, Ecchi, Romance, Slice of Life

Sakurai Shinichis one wish is for a little peace and quiet. But Uzaki Hanahis boisterous, well-endowed underclassmanhas other plans. All she wants is to hang out and poke fun at him. With the help of her chipper charm and peppy persistence, this might just be the start of a beautiful relationship!
(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)

Machiavelli and Gerrard are just one of the many names the new professor of Ceoren Academy uses to disguise his identity, and now he can add one more to his list, Professor Ludger Cherish. The real Ludger Cherish dies on board a train during a terrorist attack, making him the perfect target for a new identity. Little does the new professor know, Ludger Cherish was involved in something deep and secret. The new Professor Ludger has to be careful to not get caught by the school and the dangerous secret society.
(Source: WEBTOONS)
